index 0000000..1e4af21
--- /dev/null
+++ b/SOLUTION.md
@@ -0,0 +1,6 @@
+# Solution
+
+- The `test` recipe in `Makefile` was indented with spaces, so Make could not parse it. Replaced the spaces with the required tab.
+- `data/config.json` had a trailing comma, making it invalid JSON. Removed the trailing comma.
+- `scripts/run_checks.sh` had lost its executable permission. Restored the executable bit.
+- `scripts/run_checks.sh` used CRLF line endings, causing Linux to interpret its shebang as `/bin/bash\r`. Converted it to LF line endings.
